name: Name: Melted | BBR Generative Art
description: An artist always creates a work with his worldview and inspiration from his surroundings, so what if we humans give ideas and inspiration to the computer? What is the result of this cooperation? In my opinion, modern art is unpredictable art, art that is born of something beyond the human mind and gaze, a worldview that we have not experienced, and is narrated from the perspective of a computer and artificial intelligence.
